Forgetting Sarah Marshall;;76;;83;;R;;Struggling musician Peter Bretter (Jason Segel) is better-known as the boyfriend of TV star Sarah Marshall (Kristen Bell). After she unceremoniously dumps him, he feels lost and alone but makes a last-ditch bid to get over it by going to Hawaii. However, she and her new boyfriend (Russell Brand) are there in the same hotel.;;Romance,Comedy;;Nicholas Stoller;;2008;;Jason Segel,Kristen Bell,Mila Kunis,Russell Brand,Bill Hader,Liz Cackowski,Jack McBrayer,Taylor Wily,Da'Vone McDonald,Steve Landesberg,Jonah Hill,Paul Rudd,Kala Alexander,Branscombe Richmond,Billy Bush,Jason Bateman,William Baldwin;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/forgetting_sarah_marshall